## Invokable skills (loaded per subagent, not on boot)

Project Studio has no hard skill dependencies. Boot and resume never probe
external skills. When CoS spawns a code-heavy specialist at standard or
heavy scale, it instructs the spawn to load `graphify` (solo or combined
with a downstream analysis skill) scoped to the relevant module path.
See `project-studio/references/invokable-skills.md`.

